    {"id":"current-ws-risk-text","type":"text","x":3410,"y":1825,"width":2040,"height":140,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#a61e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"index":"n3","roundness":null,"seed":264,"version":1,"versionNonce":264,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":0,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"PARTIAL / OPEN WS BEHAVIOR\n• afterSequence is accepted on terminal.attach, but replay and a terminal-owned sequence buffer are not implemented yet.\n• terminal.detatch is currently an empty handler and is misspelled in the message discriminator.\n• terminal.command.result construction is still incomplete; connection.status.changed, redis.pubsub.message and plc.value.changed exist in the schema but are not complete end-to-end flows.\n• Socket close correctly removes Bun topic subscriptions; it does not destroy the sandbox tool or Redis connection.","fontSize":17,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"PARTIAL / OPEN WS BEHAVIOR\n• afterSequence is accepted on terminal.attach, but replay and a terminal-owned sequence buffer are not implemented yet.\n• terminal.detatch is currently an empty handler and is misspelled in the message discriminator.\n• terminal.command.result construction is still incomplete; connection.status.changed, redis.pubsub.message and plc.value.changed exist in the schema but are not complete end-to-end flows.\n• Socket close correctly removes Bun topic subscriptions; it does not destroy the sandbox tool or Redis connection.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},
    {"id":"events-title","type":"text","x":3365,"y":2160,"width":1140,"height":42,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#111827","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"index":"n4","roundness":null,"seed":265,"version":1,"versionNonce":265,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":0,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"Proposed scalable message model — attachment, requests and replayable tool events","fontSize":28,"fontFamily":2,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"Proposed scalable message model — attachment, requests and replayable tool events","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},
